{"tid":843102,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"內地稅務總局澄清　港澳台居民無需雙重納稅","createTime":"2018-10-01T01:31:08.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-01T14:22:38.000Z","uid":195944,"like":16,"dislike":34,"uniUserReply":35,"replies":[{"pid":"4c083e1376bd1be7c0360f14fcd46fd3eee7d5f6","tid":843102,"uid":195944,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-01T01:31:08.000Z","msg":"在內地長住的港澳台人士，今年9月起可申請內地居住證，一旦成功獲批，便有義務向內地政府納稅，引起關注。財政部稅務總局周日（30日）表示，當局下一步落實新個人所得稅法時，<span style=\"color: red;\">將考慮繼續對包括港澳台在內的境外人士，作出優惠安排</span>。 <br />\n<br />\n稅務總局負責人稱，現時內地政府在個人所得稅方面，對境外人士有特殊優惠。例如<span style=\"color: red;\">在內地無永久住所，但居住1年以上5年以下的人士，</span>如已在境外繳稅，相關金額將無需在內地雙重納稅，當局會考慮維持有關優惠。 <br />\n<br />\n全國人大常委會早前通過新修訂個稅法草案，確定明年1月1日起正式實施，包括向在中國境內住滿半年的居民徵收稅款，起徵點由舊稅法的每月3500元（人民幣‧下同），提高至5000元。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180930/mobile/bkn-20180930220624148-0930_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180930%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20180930220624148-0930_00822_001.html&d=IY9ik%2BbGM%2BtiGt2nohrInkbWhtBCnEJYRTWbVbFBOac%3D&h=c321d826\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180930/mobile/bkn-20180930220624148-0930_00822_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n既然攞晒福利點解唔駛交稅？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n係咪想搞港獨？ 台獨？ 澳獨？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n啲豬上到去買晒樓 住到死都唔駛交稅？ 係咪狆蟈人？<br />\n<br />\n強烈要求收依啲人重稅 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"09f66230ae87be701fd20564fe685802292d3620","tid":843102,"uid":195944,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-01T01:31:57.000Z","msg":"唔單止要交 仲要交三倍！"},{"pid":"806c5a640b1e642f974822ea8f6f67b26ea2add7","tid":843102,"uid":141151,"like":23,"dislike":0,"score":23,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-01T01:35:48.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">考慮<br />\n<br />\n考慮<br />\n<br />\n考慮<br />\n</span></span><br />\n<br />\n同埋「相關金額」渣，即係交左香港稅，扣左仲要補返夠大陸稅為止？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82897cc137e6445b5d515f724cb1aaefdc91e74d","tid":843102,"uid":64345,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-01T01:36:33.000Z","msg":"大陸政府部門成日用境外人士，根本一早當咗台港澳唔係中國一部分<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a6af1e6e1c819960a0811a3b77b5652736442e9","tid":843102,"uid":108467,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-01T01:38:16.000Z","msg":"收啦，好人好姐邊會上去住。"},{"pid":"dcd3a726cadae634a8e7fb0eb891015b1cbf945b","tid":843102,"uid":195944,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"82897cc137e6445b5d515f724cb1aaefdc91e74d","tid":843102,"uid":64345,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-01T01:36:33.000Z","msg":"大陸政府部門成日用境外人士，根本一早當咗台港澳唔係中國一部分<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-01T01:38:56.000Z","msg":"成日鼓吹港獨<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n應該將自己打靶 <br />\n<br />\n分離蟈家 叛蟈<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不得好死"},{"pid":"e3ba84cd4cb4fdec4a4a842d0ab3e8860d915863","tid":843102,"uid":83378,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-01T01:39:55.000Z","msg":"咁多大白象 要拎你錢 洗咩你交稅呀"},{"pid":"6fe87ba91d4f3f7aff5c5a18617fd81ebc40cc7f","tid":843102,"uid":149494,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-01T01:41:46.000Z","msg":"德政<br />\n準備係大灣區買樓"},{"pid":"8257948aaeaa8676a8c5fa3e245dd0905bd0252e","tid":843102,"uid":28195,"like":0,"dislike